    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Why do you say it was a failure though? Some argue that the regime was actually worse for the people and that the intervention prevented a massive humanitarian disaster. Isn't the failure of the post-war state a separate issue from the success of the actual military operation?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
